Author: mme1022
Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: White Rabbit: A Pause in the Token Sale and Cannes Film Festival Update  Dear Responsible Rebels,  As you may be aware, our token sale is being conducted in Lichtenstein which has favorable legislation for token sales and a belief in blockchain. We were notified today by the Lichtenstein FMA that they have not as of yet completed their review of our utility token, so we have been recommended to pause the token sale. We have received a legal opinion from two reputable law firms that WRT is indeed a utility token, so we look forward to receiving the FMA statement. We absolutely respect and will comply with the FMA¬¥s wish, and herewith pause the token sale. Everybody who has contributed will be refunded.   Follow this link for the full Medium post - https://medium.com/@JumpIn/a-pause-in-the-white-rabbit-token-sale-and-cannes-film-festival-update-3fde83bc25d4

Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: Hello all, shortly after deploying our smart contract integration with Wings, the Wings community asked us whether the forecast was total or for the main sale only. Thanks to their inquiries we reviewed the logic of the smart contract and discovered an issue. The smart contract was not as intended, due to miscommunication between White Rabbit and the developers. This issue is now resolved and the smart contract and forecasting redeployed to include a total forecast for both presale and main sale. You can read more in our Medium blog - in the meantime, keep being #responsiblerebels  https://medium.com/@JumpIn/wings-smart-contract-update-3948dc269a8d  https://www.wings.ai/project/0xa1d4ad346d5b32bae809ca8e3c5180e07a4020e9

Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: Hi T85083598  We are not like youtube as in no ads and we focus on feature-length films and series, not user-created content. As a plug-in, we are streaming site independent but offer more value through our partner streaming sites. We are like VOD, except there is Rabbit Hole where your purchased content is available. WingsDao, is working on doing just that.  Many well known projects have utilized Wings for evaluating their whitepaper, teams, token economics, etc.  I am glad to see WhiteRabbit is doing their part to lead the way in showing that they believe in transparency and are willing to subject themselves to the feedback from hundreds of forecasters from the WingsDao community.  Anyone can take part in this, and the rewards can be fantastic.  Just today, a reward was paid out to Wings Forecasters who evaluated a token sale from another big project who utilized Wings for evaluation and promotion. In fact, this particular reward was worth over 1 Million U.S.D. which was divided amongst the forecasters who predicted how much that project would raise.  For those who do not know, you lock Wings tokens up and make an evaluation on a project, like WhiteRabbit who offer forecasters a percentage of their tokens to all who make an evaluation.  The more Wings you have and the closer you are to the final result, the more tokens you earn from that particular project.  No matter how bad your forecast is though, you never lose your Wings and can use them to forecast on any and all projects who utilize Wings.  Hands up to WhiteRabbit for leading the way, and hopefully one day, all projects will follow their lead and help weed out bad actors or poorly designed token economics.  Thank you WhiteRabbit. Author: d2s4
Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: ICO Analysis: White Rabbit Published on April 23, 2018 By noahsayres  Verdict White Rabbit is an incredibly ambitious attempt to fix the content streaming industry. They appeared to have thought deeply about the correct way to fix the problems and also to have drawn inspiration from other brilliant but flawed attempts such as Popcorn time. Risks     Despite designing an incredibly well thought out platform, I don‚Äôt think the White Rabbit team has created strong enough incentives for consumers to actually download the plugin and begin to use White Rabbit.     Although users get an extra 5% token bonus for allowing their data to be monetized within the platform, that doesn‚Äôt strike me as a good enough sales pitch to get the average person to download this plugin and start paying content creators. -2.5     As White Rabbit themselves know well, content is king. You can create the most innovative platform, with the best features, the sleekest UI, and the perfect solution for rights holders, but if a consumer can‚Äôt watch their favorite show how and when they want to, the platform is worthless. Hulu is a perfect example of this.     The entire premise of White Rabbit is that a majority of people consuming pirated content are actually just frustrated fans who would be happy to pay for content legally if it was simply convenient and affordable for them to do so.     It was therefore incredibly puzzling that one of the terms they demanded of partnered streaming sites was to delete media content if rights holders didn‚Äôt want to participate and White Rabbit asked them to. Especially at the beginning, this could undermine White Rabbit‚Äôs entire purpose for existing and lead to users quitting the platform out of frustration.     Although ultimately this would still technically be the fault of the rights holder and entrenched industry players, I don‚Äôt see White Rabbit becoming the dominant force unless they are willing to break through the logjam and potentially face litigation from content holders early on. -3.5 Growth Potential     Incredibly low fixed token supply that should only increase in value as White Rabbit‚Äôs user base grows. +5.5     Incredibly reasonable solution to the current logjam that is streaming media.     Implemented intelligently, the incentives are aligned to allow consumers to pay for the content that they want, wherever and whenever they want to watch it.     This alone is a revolutionary breakthrough that blockchain technology enables that could radically change the entire industry. +6.5 Disposition We arrive at a score of 6/10 for White Rabbit. Although it appears to be a project with immense potential, a fantastic team, and favorable token economics, the sheer difficulty of the problems they are trying to solve adds a degree of risk to an otherwise stellar project. But to quote the whitepaper, ‚ÄúWhen an entire generation breaks the law, it shouldn¬¥t be a crime, it should be a business opportunity‚Äù -Alan R. Milligan, White Rabbit founder Proof: https://hacked.com/ico-analysis-white-rabbit/

Author: mme1022
Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: Hey Daffadile.  KYC stands for ‚ÄúKnow Your Customer".It is a process of obtaining relevant identifying information about the customers of a service. The platform that provides the service will mandate all customers to submit appropriate identification documents like photo IDs, bank accounts, credit card information, residential address, utility bills etc.  The purpose of KYC is mainly to ensure that unqualified people are precluded from using a service that they are not authorized to use. These could include minors, undocumented immigrants, or people with criminal histories. It also provides a database of information that can prove useful in an investigation by law enforcement in the event of some future criminal activity. KYC is an integral part of many online platforms such gambling and forex trading.  You are more than welcome to have a look at the legal opinion of the WR tokens sale. This document contains all the legal data of the tokens sale.  You can find more info in regards to the team members on the website and WP  ************ Jump into the rabbit hole for more updates and news!

Author: Ruthenian
Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: A new user in the Telegram channel asked if WR is a plugin. This is a frequent question. That the CEO quickly answered   ''We are not like youtube as in no ads and we focus on feature-length films and series, not user-created content. As a plug-in, we are streaming site independent, but offer more value through our partner streaming sites. You can read about them here: https://medium.com/@JumpIn/christmas-isnt-over-yet-white-rabbit-is-excited-to-announce-our-partner-streaming-sites-program-90c97fd1f89a  We are like VOD, except there is Rabbit Hole where your purchased content is available. In the rabbit hole you will have access to extras like behind the scenes, directors cut, deleted scenes, merchandise and other interaction between fans and filmmaker, created by third parties.  75% of WRT (token) goes to the content rights holder, 15% to White Rabbit and 10% to partner streaming sites.   It is not like tipeee - you initially pay a fixed cost for content although we will allow CRH also to make available such a model. However, if it is a film/series where you want to additionally award one of the artists, that is possible too.  You can read more in our Whitepaper available at www.whiterabbit.one''  I hope this would clear up any confusion for those wondering the same

Author: Ruthenian
Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: Q. Is White Rabbit going to the source of the movies? A. Its a three pronged approach. I am a producer myself, and work closely with sales agents and distributors who have libraries of films - some that have unsold territories, some that are being pirated to the extent that WR is a solution for them to collect revenue from p2p streaming. So I am talking to my contacts to secure rights for WR. Furthermore, the token itself WRT allows you the fans to change the industry, 1 film at a time. I will forward my previous message in this regard. Finally, should we reach the hard cap for the ICO, some fund will be allocated to securing streaming rights for flagship content, films and series - Alan (CEO)

Author: FreakMighty
Title: [ANN][SALE] White Rabbit - A New Digital Streaming Reality. PRESALE LIVE!
Body: Thanks so much for engaging!  White Rabbit is a browser plug-in that recognizes the content you watch, without forcing you to subscribe to anyone site. By separating distribution from payment, White Rabbit offers one payment system, but infinite viewing experiences.  Netflix has turned into a studio more than a content distributor per se. Content that people want is not available to them via platforms so they seek it out via piracy methods. Platforms don't offer the content that people want, and if they do, more often than not they are subscribed to a competing platform and not willing to pay a subscription to a second platform for one TV show or movie they would like to see. It's easier and more convenient to download for free.   With White Rabbit plugin you are not restricted with these limitations, you can choose to watch what you like and pay seamlessly for the content you digest without a binding subscription fee. Pay for what you watch, and do so easily, knowing the content creator is being duly rewarded in the process. This is what White Rabbit represents   As a plug-in we are platform independent, meaning fans choose the streaming site they prefer to stream from. White Rabbit merely recognizes content and allow users to offer tokens to copyright holders.  The Rabbit Hole is the user¬¥s film library - It offers additional content to fans. From behind-the-scenes, to merchandise to interaction with other fans and filmmakers.  Our team is balanced between all the stakeholders. We are filmmakers, software entrepreneurs, blockchain developers and first and foremost fans. That¬¥s what makes us responsible rebels.
